data.name: TextBox1.Text
data.value:
Poppy was found on a very busy street as a tiny kitten all alone. She was easy to catch because she was so hungry. She was a quiet kitten, no trouble. Poppy is shy until she gets to know you and is then very loving. She loves cuddles, she snuggles into your neck and purrs. She is vey attentive and will follow you everywhere.
Poppy does not like other cats at all. She gets upset if they come near and they tend to pick on her. Because she is little shy. Poppy needs a quiet environment with older people and no other cats.
Poppy is medium haired so easy to groom. She loves her toys, is very sweet and loyal as has no health issues at all.
